INSERT INTO public.tojung (id,num,total,jan,feb,mar,apr,may,jun,jul,aug,sep,oct,nov,"dec",created_at,nation) VALUES (303,'005','âœ¨ 1. 2026 Overall Fortune
The year 2026 brings precious opportunities like blessed rain from clear skies. Wealth awaits in the eastern and northern directions, so beginning endeavors or forming connections in those areas will bring great assistance. Utilizing the spring energy is crucial, as missing this timing may make it difficult to grasp good opportunities. While you have the will to move forward, you may sometimes feel your strength is insufficient. There are many things you wish to accomplish, but this is a period where they won''t come easily, so maintaining patience and preparing step by step is advisable. Self-restraint, prudence, and keeping within your means are the core virtues for this year.

âœ¨ 2. ğŸ’° Wealth and Financial Fortune
Your 2026 financial fortune holds great opportunities in the eastern and northeastern directions. In February and March, unexpected wealth may arrive, but keeping it won''t be easy, requiring careful financial management. Since this is a fortune of gaining first but potentially losing later, focusing on stable savings rather than large investments is wise. In July and August, opportunities to gain wealth through cooperation with others exist, but you must carefully choose your associates. Wrong relationships can bring financial loss, so be especially cautious. Toward year''s end, focus on financial organization and avoid excessive spending.

âœ¨ 3. ğŸ† Career and Promotion Fortune
Career fortune shows better flow in the second half than the first. The first half brings many difficulties and obstacles, but steady effort will bear fruit in the second half. In May and June, misunderstandings may arise in relationships with colleagues or superiors, so be careful with words and act prudently. In September and October, work achievements will be recognized, earning positive evaluations. If considering entrepreneurship or job changes, the second half is more favorable, especially November being the optimal time. However, seeking advice from trustworthy people rather than making unilateral decisions is the key to success.

âœ¨ 4. â¤ï¸ Love and Marriage Fortune
For singles, the spring months of March and April are periods to meet good matches. People met in eastern or northeastern directions have high potential for developing into good relationships. Married couples may face communication difficulties with spouses in the first half, requiring patience and resolution through dialogue. In June and July, emotional conflicts may arise, requiring careful words and actions. Hastily believing and acting on others'' words can crack relationships, so be cautious. The second half brings relationship stability and harmonious times.

âœ¨ 5. ğŸ¥ Health Fortune
Overall, this is a year requiring health attention. Especially during spring and autumn seasonal changes, immunity may weaken, requiring special health care. In April and May, beware of fatigue accumulation from overwork and get sufficient rest. In August and September, digestive system issues may arise, so maintain proper eating habits and avoid overeating. Stress management is important, with regular exercise and meditation being helpful. In November and December, be cautious of respiratory illnesses and ventilate indoor spaces frequently.

âœ¨ 6. ğŸ‘¥ Relationship Fortune
This is a year requiring prudence in relationships. In the first half, easily believing others'' words can lead to losses, so choose associates carefully. In May and June, possibilities of getting caught in gossip exist, so be careful with words and avoid unnecessary disputes. In July and August, you may be hurt by close people, so maintaining appropriate distance is advisable. The second half brings new connections and opportunities to meet helpful benefactors. Building good relationships with people from eastern and northern directions proves beneficial.

âœ¨ 7. ğŸ“š Academic and Self-Development Fortune
This is a period requiring consistency in academics and self-development. Rather than expecting quick results, setting long-term plans and executing them step by step is better. March and April are suitable times to start new studies, but strengthen your will to avoid giving up midway. In July and August, concentration may decrease, so organize your learning environment and maintain regular schedules. In October and November, previous efforts bear fruit, yielding good results. If planning certification acquisition or new skill learning, the second half is more favorable.','January requires a cautious start despite being the year''s beginning. You may feel frustrated by blocked matters, but good energy awaits afterward. Like a golden pig entering your home, patience will bring good results. You may feel others trying to block your path, so carefully discern surrounding people''s intentions.

Wealth fortune is unstable. Avoiding large expenditures and focusing on savings is wise. At work, new projects or business changes may occur, but don''t rush and prepare carefully. Health-wise, be cautious of winter colds and flu, and focus on strengthening immunity.

Relationships require prudence. Don''t easily believe others'' words and prioritize your own judgment. The eastern direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being light gray and white. Abandoning haste and calmly starting the month will bring better opportunities next month.','February brings wealth energy from the northeast. Making friends in that direction can bring wealth, so actively expand your network. When planning big things, you can receive others'' help, but pay special attention to health. Avoid excessive schedules and get sufficient rest.

Wealth fortune gradually improves. Small unexpected income may arise, so welcome opportunities with a positive mind. At work, cooperation with colleagues is important, so strive to maintain good relationships.

Health management is very important. Avoid overwork and maintain regular lifestyle habits. Especially pay attention to sleep quality and appropriately relieve stress. In relationships, you can form good connections with northeastern people. Lucky colors are brown and beige, with lucky numbers being 2 and 8.','March brings auspicious fortune later despite initial difficulties. Meeting benefactors brings extremely fortunate destiny to fulfill aspirations, so actively participate in positive encounters. Like spring energy reviving all things, this is a good time for new beginnings.

Wealth fortune shows gradually rising flow. If small investment or business opportunities arise, proceed after careful review. At work, you may be assigned new tasks or projects, and sincere effort brings good evaluations.

Health-wise, beware of spring seasonal colds and focus on strengthening immunity. Increasing outdoor activities to boost physical vitality is advisable. In relationships, this month has high potential for meeting benefactors, so actively participate in gatherings or events. Eastern and southeastern directions are auspicious, with lucky colors being light green and pink.','April is an auspicious month when lucky stars shine on your door. Wealth and treasures enter through the door in a joyful period, but be careful in all matters as what begins auspiciously may turn inauspicious later. Wealth lies eastward, and even if gained, may be lost again, making it difficult to keep all profits.

Wealth fortune looks good but expenditure management is important. What comes in also goes out abundantly, so practice planned consumption. Decide large investments carefully, and if possible, seek expert advice.

At work, achievements may be recognized with praise or rewards. However, don''t become arrogant and maintain humble attitudes. Health is good but avoid overwork and maintain fitness through moderate exercise. The western direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being yellow and gold.','May is a month when wrong associations can bring losses. Like an angler losing their fishing rod, you may lose precious things, so be especially careful in relationships. However, lowering yourself and being humble brings joyful events, with all hundred matters proceeding smoothly.

Wealth fortune is average. Don''t harbor excessive greed, be satisfied with what you have, and steadily save. Don''t easily fall for others'' proposals or investment solicitations, and judge carefully.

At work, relationships with colleagues affect work performance. Work cooperatively and show respectful attitudes toward others. Health-wise, pay attention to the digestive system, avoid overeating, and eat regularly. The northern direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being black and navy blue.','June is a month when you shouldn''t believe others'' words as they are. There are losses from wrong associations, so selectively listen to words or don''t listen at all. Otherwise, regrets may arise or unexpected expenses may occur.

Wealth fortune is unstable. Be especially careful as believing others'' words and investing can bring losses. Making all financial decisions only after thorough personal review is safe.

At work, be careful not to get caught in rumors or gossip, and focus only on your own work. Avoid unnecessary chatter and act prudently. Health requires stress management, so strive to maintain peace of mind. The eastern direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being blue and white.','July finally brings wealth providing peace of mind. Wealth lies eastward, and even if gained, some will be lost. What was gained from ventures cannot all be digested, so don''t be greedy. Gaining first and losing later may result in outcomes worse than the beginning.

Wealth fortune improves but management is important. Keep incoming wealth well and reduce unnecessary expenditures. Focusing on savings rather than investments is wise.

At work, projects may conclude or achievements be recognized. However, don''t try to monopolize all credit and share with colleagues. Health-wise, beware of summer heat and maintain sufficient hydration. The eastern direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being green and light green.','August brings secret worries in your heart. You may feel all worldly matters are like dreams. If no solutions appear, financial losses may instead occur, so don''t push forcefully and wait for the right time.

Wealth fortune is ordinary. Don''t have high expectations and be satisfied with maintaining status quo. New investments or businesses are premature, so waiting for the next opportunity is wise.

At work, you may experience stagnation, but this too shall pass. Do your best in your current position and use this as a period to build internal strength. Health requires mental and physical stability, with activities like meditation or yoga being helpful. The southern direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being purple and violet.','September brings gossip and disturbances. Those who slander you are likely wrongly associated people, so be careful in dealing with people. Continuing to associate with unvirtuous people may lead to unmanageable problems.

Wealth fortune is poor, so avoid new investments or expenditures as much as possible. Be especially careful with financial transactions with others, and absolutely refrain from guarantees or lending.

At work, stress from relationships may be significant. Avoid unnecessary disputes and focus only on work. Health-wise, beware of headaches or indigestion from stress and get sufficient rest. The northeastern direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being gray and silver.','October brings unfavorable fortune with many problems in all matters. Don''t be too forward, maintain composure, and stay quiet. Even vigorously pursuing desired matters brings no results and only wasted effort, so abandon excessive greed.

Wealth fortune is poor, so avoid investments or business expansion and focus on maintaining status quo. Reducing unnecessary expenditures and developing saving habits is advisable.

At work, focus on finishing current tasks rather than starting new ones. Don''t set excessive goals and concentrate on realistically achievable things. Health-wise, avoid overwork and maintain regular lifestyle. The western direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being white and ivory.','November requires fire caution. Fearing physical and mental harm, pay special attention to safety. If seeking wealth, you must actively meet people by foot. Staying only at home won''t allow grasping opportunities, so be proactive.

Wealth fortune yields as much as effort invested. Don''t wait passively but actively seek opportunities. However, prioritize safety and avoid excessive adventures.

At work, there may be many field visits or business trips, through which new opportunities can be discovered. Approach work with proactive attitudes but thoroughly follow safety rules. Health-wise, beware of accidents or injuries and be careful handling fire. The southeastern direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being red and orange.','December may bring people among close friends who wish to harm you. Don''t go north and stay quietly nearby. Resting from ongoing work will surely bring harm, so finishing through to the end is important.

Wealth fortune is poor, so avoid new investments or businesses. Use this as a period to wrap up the year and prepare for next year. Minimizing expenditures and checking finances is advisable.

At work, focus on year-end tasks and postpone new work to next year. In relationships, be careful of conflicts with close people and maintain appropriate distance. Health-wise, avoid year-end overwork and get sufficient rest. The eastern direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being gold and silver.','2025-03-02 03:02:00.895174+00','e');
